                <h3 class="staff_list__subheader">President</h3>
                <p class="staff_list__text">Matt started Boulevard Building Group, LLC in 2010 with the intent to bring unique styling and quality construction to middle Tennessee.  Growing up around construction, Matt is a second generation homebuilder who has lived in Middle Tennessee for over 20 years. Matt graduated from University of Tennessee – Knoxville in Finance and currently lives in Fairview with his wife and two children where he enjoys cooking, hiking and music!</p>
