                <p class="staff_list__text">Amanda has been part of the BLVD team since 2015.  Amanda handles office and job site coordination regarding selections, deliveries and scheduling.  Amanda graduated from UT – Knoxville with a BA in Political Science & has her MBA from Middle Tennessee State University in Management and currently lives with her husband in west Nashville where she enjoys yardwork, walking her dog, and staying active!</p>
              </div>
